## Verification Plan

### Manual Test (Single Camera)
1. Run the local tracker on the provided crowd video:
```bash
python run_tracker.py --source Shopping_People_Commerce_Mall_Many_Crowd_Walking_Free_Stock_video_footage_YouTube_360P.mp4 --output tracked_botsort.mp4 --device cpu
```
2. Verify that bounding boxes are stable (no stuttering, no ballooning) and IDs remain consistent.

